## Commercial License

For commercial use without AGPL-3.0 requirements (e.g., proprietary modifications, SaaS without source disclosure), a commercial license is available.

### What requires a Commercial License?

- Running SafeScoring as a commercial SaaS without sharing your modifications
- Integrating SafeScoring into proprietary software
- Removing SafeScoring branding/attribution
- Using the SAFE methodology database for commercial purposes without attribution

### Commercial License Benefits

- No copyleft requirements
- Priority support
- Access to premium features
- Custom integrations
- SLA guarantees

### Pricing

Contact us for commercial licensing:
- Email: license@safescoring.com
- Website: https://safescoring.com/enterprise

